// Goal: (r1@ == v@ && r2@ == v@) ==> r1 == r2 for Vec<u8>.
    // Vec equality at spec level is NOT extensional w.r.t. @ view in Verus.
    // No axiom bridges view-equality to SMT-level Vec equality, so this
    // implication is not provable from the given premises alone.
    assert(r1@ == v@ ==> r2@ == v@ ==> r1@ =~= r2@);
